column5: Fascinating. Oh well, that is all I have for you. Proceed with caution. Don't trust her, even if she is the, ha. Fairest of them all.

column4: 'You are not sure what that means now, but the Narrator assures you that it will make sense in due time.'

column5: There is much to doubt in a world that seems like it was simply... made for you.
Good luck, and remember: we all end where we begin.
